
Overview of noun revolver

The noun revolver has 2 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                       
1. (4) revolver, six-gun, six-shooter -- (a pistol with a revolving cylinder (usually having six chambers for bullets))
2. revolving door, revolver -- (a door consisting of four orthogonal partitions that rotate about a central pivot; a door designed to equalize the air pressure in tall buildings)
